 measurements\nof three more Type 1 AGNs newly observed with the Keck interferometer, as well\nas the second epoch measurements for three other AGNs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 16:47:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
