~1) cannot be supported. In contrast, our previous results on E-mini S&P 500\nFutures Contracts and on major commodity future contracts are upheld.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2013 14:23:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2013 10:59:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Jul 2014 14:49:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-04"}
